					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is a really fantastic SCP, definitely one of my favorites. The sense of barely containing it and possibly being unable to contain it in the near future due to all its disturbing effects is well done. One minor suggestion: change &quot;photographic memory&quot; to &quot;eidetic memory&quot;, as the latter is the more accurate scientific term. Otherwise great stuff.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
