					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I just got my account so this is my first time saying really anything on this great big site of anomalies.</p> <p>This is really one of my favorites(my account might be new, but I have been exploring scps for about 2 years now), it's ability to strengthen/corrupt while contained, possession and transformation of containment area really made this one shine to me.</p> <p>A idea that might work with this is returning scp 35 to where it was in Venice to maybe hold the seeming curse at bay(?), or force feeding the host of scp 35 a heaping helping of scp 666&#160;1/2-J, either would make a great addition to what is already amazing.</p> 
